law.history: Repealed 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 82, sec. 22, effective July 15, 1998; amended ch. 154, sec. 48, effective July 15, 1998. -- Created 1988 Ky. Acts ch. 5, sec. 3, effective 15, 1988.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Custody and supervision of state employee benefit fund -- Duties -- Moneys credited to fund -- Special reserve -- Investments -- Reports.
metadata.lrc-note: (7/15/98) Under KRS 446.260, the repeal of this section in 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 82 prevails over its amendment in 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 154.
